title: Tennen Mousou Shiyouchuu
sinopse:
Keiichi is a pure-hearted boy having lot of sexual fantasies. Chihoru is a rude but feminine girl. This book describes sexual fantasies between Keiichi and Chihoru. They are always thinking of making love.

(Source: MU)

Included one-shot: Ka-ge-ki ni Renai Kakumei (Radical Love Revolution)
